title: Refrigerator Flipper Assembly
description: Refrigerator Flipper Assembly PartSelect Number PS5575408 Manufacturer Part Number DA97-12947A This flipper assembly (part number DA97-12947A) is for refrigerators. Flipper assembly DA97-12947A creates an airtight seal between the doors on a French-door refrigerator. Safely store any food that could deteriorate while the power is off and unplug the refrigerator before installing this part.
